# Keep the build context small AND prevent host-built artifacts from clobbering the clean
# installs done inside the image. Critically: stage 1 runs `npm ci` and THEN `COPY frontend/`,
# so without excluding node_modules the host's (possibly Windows-built) node_modules would
# overwrite the freshly installed Linux one and break the build.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
.git
.gitignore
.venv
**/.env*
.claude
